The following is a list of all the items, organised by level, that are needed for [[Treasure Trails/Guide/Emote clues|Emote clues]]. The items in a list are alphabetically organised. For items that require multiple items, the quantity is given, so that you know exactly how many items you are going to need for each clue type; this is useful for stocking up items when making [[STASH units]]. When no quantity is given to an item it means it only needs one item for that clue level by default. Note that one item in the list of one level of a clue, can also appear in the list of another level of a clue. Don't forget this when stocking up on items!

